AreaRangeAreaId.description: The area that the address range is to be found within.

AreaRangeEffect.description: Subnets subsumed by ranges either trigger the advertisement of the indicated summary (advertiseMatching) or result in the subnet's not being advertised at all outside the area.

AreaRangeMask.description: The subnet mask that pertains to the net or subnet.

AreaRangeNet.description: The IP address of the net or subnet indicated by the range.
